    <h1> Select Car reviews</h1>
    <p>For car buyers in 2025, a fundamental decision involves the vehicle's powertrain, with options ranging from conventional internal combustion engines to advanced hybrid systems and fully electric motors, each offering distinct performance and efficiency benefits.</p>

    <section>
        <h2>Internal combustion engine</h2>
        <p>For drivers prioritizing long-distance travel and rapid refueling, the conventional internal combustion engine remains a compelling choice. Its key benefit lies in unparalleled range and convenience, supported by a vast, established network of fueling stations.</p>
