        <h2>Fully electric motor</h2>
        <p>The primary benefit of electric vehicles lies in their revolutionary efficiency and performance. By harnessing electric power, EVs deliver significant savings on fuel and maintenance, eliminating routine oil changes and reducing operational costs.</p>
        
