        <h2>Hybrid systems</h2>
        <p>Hybrid vehicles offer a masterful balance, seamlessly blending the key benefits of both powertrains to eliminate traditional compromises. They provide superior fuel efficiency and reduced emissions in stop-and-go city driving by utilizing electric power, while simultaneously eliminating range anxiety with a ready-to-use gasoline engine for longer journeys.</p>
